---
title: Roast Pork Medallions with Sweet Potato Mash and Peppercorn Sauce
description: Peppercorn sauce is a traditional accompaniment for steak but it goes great with pork too. We've added some sweet potato mash and broccoli florets on the side for a plateful that's colourful and delicious. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roast-pork-medallions-9dbc864d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/roast-pork-medallions-5cf8e61f.pdf
servings: 2
nutrition:
